(thirdQuint)Pedometer and Exercise Study in Prostate Cancer Patients With Hormonal Therapy.

 To evaluate effectiveness of regular exercise and well-being all patients will complete questionnaires about sexual function (IIEF-15) and quality of life.

 We will also perform at each visits anthropometrics measurement of waist, leg and arm, weight and vital signs.

 Biochemical analysis and prostatic specific antigen will be done periodically.

